quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  41,39,"Hino jeyaa e Ma'andeeji makko …óin, tawde a nji'ay leydi ndin no yoori. Si wonii Min njippinii ndiyam to…ďo e mayri, ndi dilla ndi fontoo. Awa nguurnitu…óo ndi on, pellet, ko wuurnitoowo maay…ďe …ďen, tawde pellet, ko O kattan…óo haka hu'unde."
  41,40,"Pellet, oo√Īotoo…ďe …ďeen e aayeeje Amen …óeen, …ďe vuu…óotaako Min. E ko feroytee…óo on ka Yiite …ďuri mo∆ī∆īude kaa ko aroyoowo on √Ďalnde Darngal hino hoolii? NGollee ko paala…óon, ko pellet, Homo reeni ko ngolloton kon."
  41,41,"Yeddu…ďe …ďeen Alqur'aana tuma nde arnoo e ma…ď…ďe, pellet noon, ko nde deftere teddunde [foolnde];"
  41,42,"mehre iwrantaa nde ye'eso mayre, wonaa …ďaawo mayre. Ko jipporiinde immorde ka √Ďee√Īo, jettinii…óo On."
  41,43,"A wi'aaka si wonaa ko Nulaa…ďe adinoo…ďe ma …ďen mbi'anoo. Pellet, Joomi maa, ko O Jom yaafuyee, e Jom lepte mu'usuu…óe."
  41,44,"Si Min mba…óuno nde janngeteende e haala ajami, …ďe wi'atno: "Ko ha…óno aayeeje mayre …óen fensitee? E nde wonat e haala ajami, [Nulaa…óo] on wona aarabuujo?" Maaku: "Kayre wonan'de gooŇč…óin…ďe …ďen, ko nde peewal e cellal". ∆Āe ngooŇč…óinaa …ďen kan, noto hino e noppi ma…ď…ďe …óin, kayre ko nde ni…ďe e dow ma…ď…ďe; …ďen hino noddiree e nokku wo…ó…óu…óo."
  41,45,"GooŇč…óii Min ngokkii Muusaa Deftere ndeen, nde luutondira e mayre. Si wonaano Konngol ardinoongol immorde ka Joomi maa, hakkunde ma…ď…ďe √Īaaweteno. Kam…ďe kan, pellet, hi…ďe e sikke sikkitii…óo nde."
  41,46,"Kala gollu…óo ko mo∆ī∆īi, ko fii hoore-makko; kala kadi bonnu…óo, yantat e makko. Joomi maa ciforaani won'de, too√Īoowo jiyaa…ďe …ďen."